column5: I have tomorrow off, staying at a friends tonight, gonna try some bassin in the area, thinkin of Lower Buckhorn (need a boat launch location) any thought, tips on this area. is Lower a good choice, I am open to suggestions.    Thanyou, Grrrog
Rice Lake, Indian River outlet area, lots of bass You can launch right out side of Keene at the river or at Serpent Mounds
you can launch right in the town of buckhorn. three castles has a launch... sunrise resort also has one
